{
  "stem": "3341.4",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And suddenly I noticed coming towards the field-- because that was flat fields there-- I notice that there are coming soldiers, who are different color.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because German army was in grey, and the Russians were in green.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But that was-- you wouldn't have a clue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was Malinovsky army.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was the third Russian army, which occupied Hungary, part of Yugoslavia, Romania, and they came to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's-- Malinovsky army was the third worst supplied army ever, because it consisted of criminal element.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In Russian-- Russia, especially Stalin's regime-- they had no interest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They put them on the worst spots to decimate them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because they were the un-- unwanted element in the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had two best armies, which went over Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the other one went through Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have seen that this must be already the Russians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had the short machine guns, the [RUSSIAN], which are typical for not for you, but for me I knew it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- the two peasant boys, they were hiding behind the, the manure and the straw heaps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was the big hero because, for me it was liberation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I jumped out, and I put my hands up and started to shout in Russian, don't shoot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't shoot, I am a spy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I want to, and I want to see-- because I knew that the Russians, they shoot first and ask questions only after.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to concoct some sort of a story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first Russian soldiers who came, really, he had a bayonet on his gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he swore to high heaven.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, you are spy?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said very nasty words, which I understood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, when you speak Slovak, you can understand Polish, you can understand also Russian.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
